<p>
<b>From North</b><br>

(Alternate directions from North included below.)

<p>
<blockquote>
Take the 405 South to the 73 South. <br>
<br>
Take the University exit. <br>
<br>
Left onto University.<br>
<br>
Right onto California, which takes you into UCI.<br>
<br>
Pull over on California as soon as you enter UCI and
purchase a permit at the automated machine ($4 - quarters or $1 bills).
This permit enables you to park for the whole day.<br>
<br>
Proceed forward.<br>
<br>
Go through the intersection at West Peltason Drive (was: Bridge Rd.).<br>
<br>
Go through the lighted intersection at Bison.<br>
<br>
Go left at the second stop sign (Gabrielino Rd.) and park in lot 18C.<br>
<br>
As you enter, use the portion of the lot on the left. 
When you turn into that part of the lot, you will be 
facing the Engineering Gateway building.
</blockquote>

