<HR>

<p>

<b>From South</b><br>

<blockquote>
Take the 405 North to the University/Jeffrey exit. <br>
<br>
Left onto University (it's Jeffrey if you go right). <br>
<br>
Left onto Culver. <br>
<br>
Right onto Campus. <br>
<br>
Left onto East Peltason Drive (was: Berkeley Dr.), which takes you into UCI.<br>
<br>
Pull over on East Peltason Drive as soon as you enter UCI and purchase a 
permit at the automated machine ($4 - quarters or $1 bills).
This permit enables you to park for the whole day.<br>
<br>
Proceed forward.<br>
<br>
Go through the lighted intersection at Pereira Rd. <br>
<br>
Go right at the second stop sign (Gabrielino Rd.), and park in lot 18C. <br>
<br>
As you enter, use the portion 
of the lot on the left. When you turn into that part of the lot, you will be 
facing the Engineering Gateway building.
</blockquote>

<p>

<HR>

<p>

<!-- <b> Alternate Directions from North</b><br> -->
<b> Directions from North</b><br>

<blockquote>
Take the 405 South to the Jamboree exit. <br>
<br>
Right onto Jamboree. <br>
<br>
Left onto Campus. <br>
<br>
Go past <b> West</b> Peltason Drive.<br><br>
Right onto <b>East</b> Peltason Drive (was: Berkeley Dr.) which takes 
you into UCI.<br>
<br>
Pull over on East Peltason Drive as soon as you enter UCI and purchase 
a permit at the automated machine ($4 - quarters or $1 bills).
This permit enables you to park for the whole day.<br>
<br>
Proceed forward through the lighted intersection at Pereira Rd. <br>
<br>
Go right at the second stop sign (Gabrielino Rd.), and park in lot 18C. <br>
<br>
As you enter, use the portion 
of the lot on the left. When you turn into that part of the lot, you will be 
facing the Engineering Gateway building.
</blockquote>

